item.title: Meet the Team
item.dc:creator: Seth
item.content:encoded:
Meet the Team

Get to know a little bit about the team.

Cream City Creative was founded in 2012. It is co-owned by Becky Gahart, Matt Cordier, Seth McGathey, and Scott Parker. Each member of the team brings a different, unique specialty to the table. Becky is UX and UI specialists. Matt takes care of our graphics and design. Seth handles SEO optimization and plug-in support. Scott’s role is site administration and making sure things are done in a timely, efficient manner.

Each team member at Cream City Creative has overlapping skill sets. This synergy is what enables us to tackle large scale projects with such a small team. As a business owner there are several advantages to working with a small, tight knit company. With larger companies you may have to wait for feedback to trickle down through the ranks. At Cream City Creative all team members are in close proximity allowing changes to happen more quickly and saving you time and money. We realize feedback is key when making a clients vision into a functioning website. In light of this we offer consulting and feedback sessions throughout the build process.

item.title: Products
item.dc:creator: Seth
item.content:encoded:
Digital Business Products

Cream City Creative works with you to provide the best tools for growing your business. We offer options to get you up and running fast. If your business requires a more complex solution, our experience team can help you craft the perfect presentation. Our websites adhere to the latest web standards while ensuring they work across all devices and browsers.

Basic Website $199

Perfect Online Business Card

Fast Turn Around Time

Responsive and Mobile Friendly

Basic CMS Training

Web Analytics and SEO Audit

1 Month Support

Contact Us Cream City Custom Website Starting at $999

Fully Customized Business Solution

High Level Consultation

Custom Design/Client Feedback Sessions

Extensive UX Testing

Full Service Web Analytics and SEO Audit

Extended Support

Contact Us

Basic Website

Our Basic Website Package is the perfect way to get your online presence up and running. We offer fast turn around time and one month of additional support. When we pass the key over you will have the knowledge and tools to maintain images, blog posts, and even create your own pages for special promotions! As with all our sites, our Basic Website Package will look great on any device. You have tools to monitor your web traffic and each site is optimized for Google's search engines.

Cream City Custom

Our Cream City Custom Website Package can help take your business to the big leagues. It starts with a high level consultation process. We dig deep to understand your business ideals and goals. Each site is specially crafted to support your vision. After we have this essential understand start drafting our design. With several checkpoints along the way we ensure that you get the site of your dreams. After the site is developed we go the extra mile with extensive user testing. The result is a distinctive site that thrives in real world application.

Featured Partners

At the end of the day, every business wants technology that "just works." It's our goal at Cream City Creative to understand your business and provide you with the most timely, elegant solution. We do our job well so you can focus on what matters most to you. Nothing makes us happier than seeing a business achieve success through one of our digital solutions. We are proud to have worked with some outstanding companies.

This will allow us to quickly reference past communications with you saving you time. If you are having trouble getting in contact with them or lost their email please just reference the project we are working with you on so that we can quickly get you connected with your original contact.
